ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: If someone is interested to know one of ancient languages that is still spoken today connecting its nations to their civilization, this course is probably one of the best to take, especially with the fact that the instructor herself is Persian, and the latter is truly an important factor to be taught good and clear language.
